text: Enjoy Poconos Mountain Biking in the Lehigh Gorge State Park on the world famous Lehigh Gorge Trail, then go Whitewater Rafting or Kayaking (https://t.co/AIlo0c8uNt) on that very same river!
Whitewater Rafting and Mountain Biking Adventure Combo Tours (https://t.co/AIlo0c8uNt)
The Lehigh Gorge Rail Trail (https://t.co/uswrIeA3ms) is a downhill, scenic, state-park maintained rail trail, that follows the amazing Class 3+ Lehigh River (https://t.co/AIlo0c8uNt).
Click here for our whitewater rafting prices (https://t.co/AIlo0c8uNt).

The best valued, most adrenaline pumping, whitewater rafting and kayaking (https://t.co/AIlo0c8uNt) adventures on the Lehigh River are with us! You will have the best service, most value and the thrill of your life! Get ready for the best day you'll have all year!
Things to do in the Poconos like whitewater rafting, picturesque mountain biking and JEEP Hiking Tours are what makes the Poconos so special.
